11 SECTION 12. IC 32-28-15-1, AS ADDED BY P.L.62-2024,
12 SECTION 1, IS AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE
13 JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 1. (a) Except as otherwise provided in this
14 chapter, this chapter does not apply to a residential real estate service
15 agreement entered into before March 15, 2024.
16 (b) This chapter does not apply to any of the following:
